                  , and affixed to a building of his, feloniously did cut, with intent to steal it
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18150405-122-person1079">
                  THOMAS 
                  DUGGIN
               <interp inst="t18150405-122-person1079" type="surname" value="DUGGIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150405-122-person1079" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
