            . The house where this lead was cut is <placeName id="t18150405-122-crimeloc662">No. 21, Short's-gardens, Drury-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18150405-122-crimeloc662" type="placeName" value="No. 21, Short's-gardens, Drury-lane"></interp>
